\f0\fs46 \cf0 Best Baked Apples with Raisins and Walnuts\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\ql\qnatural

\b\fs32 \cf0 Serves 6\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\ql\qnatural

\i\b0 \cf0 If you don\'92t have an ovenproof skillet, transfer the browned apples to a 13- by 9-inch baking dish and bake as directed. The recipe calls for 7 apples; 6 are left whole and 1 is diced and added to the filling. Serve the apples with vanilla ice cream, if desired.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\ql\qnatural

